### 7. File Upload (S3) Is Completely Non-Functional
[s3.ts](file:///Users/mose/Printhub_Antigravity_Audit/printhub_africa/lib/s3.ts)

Both [getUploadUrl()](file:///Users/mose/Printhub_Antigravity_Audit/printhub_africa/lib/s3.ts#9-18) and [getSignedDownloadUrl()](file:///Users/mose/Printhub_Antigravity_Audit/printhub_africa/lib/s3.ts#19-26) are TODO stubs that return empty strings. The schema has `UploadedFile` model with 11 file types, but **no user can actually upload files**.

For a print shop where customers upload artwork (STL, AI, PDF, PSD, etc.), this is a core business requirement that doesn't work.

