[getClient()](file:///Users/mose/Printhub_Antigravity_Audit/printhub_africa/lib/sanity.ts#8-13) returns `null`. [getBlogPosts()](file:///Users/mose/Printhub_Antigravity_Audit/printhub_africa/lib/sanity.ts#14-21) returns `[]`. Blog/content features don't work.

